      "beast_baseline": "Wait, \"goblin market\" and \"goblin's bargain\"? I'm just asking about the biology of bread. Can you stick to the scientific explanation of the pH shift and the enzymatic breakdown? I want to understand how the amylase activity works in relation to that acidity.",
